{"word":"Sodomites","slug":"sodomites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sodomites</b> Inhabitants of Sodom.<br/> Wickedness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=14'>Gen 19:14</a><br/> Destroyed by fire as a judgment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=25'>Gen 19:25</a><br/> To be judged according to opportunity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=24'>Mat 11:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=12'>Luk 10:12</a><br/> A proverbial term of reproach applied to those who practice sodomy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=17'>Deu 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=24'>1Ki 14:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=12'>1Ki 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=46'>1Ki 22:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=7'>2Ki 23:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=36&verse=14'>Job 36:14</a><br/> The word &#187;harlot&#171; is the translation of a Hebrew feminine form of the word translated elsewhere &#187;sodomite&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=38&verse=22'>Gen 38:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=17'>Deu 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=14'>Hos 4:14</a><br/><a href='S:Sodomy'>Sodomy</a>"}]}